snippet.title: Rebel Galaxy Outlaw Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Double Damage Games is proud to announce Rebel Galaxy Outlaw

http://rebelgalaxyoutlaw.com

Juno Markev thought she was out, on the right side of the law for once.
Circumstances have conspired to drag her back in, and things have been going badly ever since.
That's the thing with circumstances, though.
They can always get a whole lot worse.

Welcome to Rebel Galaxy Outlaw

Our cinematic was animated by the talented folks at TItmouse-

Titmouse is an Emmy award-winning animation production company known for series such as Venture Bros., Big Mouth, Superjail!, Black Dynamite, Niko and the Sword of Light, Little Big Awesome, and Metalocalypse and more. 

Visit them at and check out more of their amazing work at

http://titmouse.net 

And check out their 2018 reel at

http://titmouse.net/work-titmouse-lord-of-shapes-2018-reel/
